column14: I got the coffee nude collection. The colors range from a lighter brown to a very dark chocolate. The darkest color is probably too dark for my taste and I would not call it "nude." Nonetheless, I really like this lipstick. It goes on smoothly and feels moisturizing and soothing to the lips. The application does not last if you are eating or drinking, however, but can be touched up when needed.  The bottoms of the lipstick containers have color coded stickers for easy identification of colors. Overall, I really like this lipstick collection, just wish the application lasted a bit longer.
